Key comma A 4 StartOrWarpTo gcalctool gcalctool

DestroyFunc StartOrWarpTo
AddToFunc   StartOrWarpTo
+ I Any ($0,iconic) Next ($0,iconic) Iconify
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) ThisWindow ($0,focused) Iconify
+ I Any ($0,!focused) Next ($0,!focused) WarpToWindow 50 50
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Exec exec $1 $2 $3
#+ D Next ($0,focused) Close

#+ I Any ($0,iconic) Next ($0,iconic) Iconify
Key y A 4 JOE Qterm qterm

DestroyFunc RaiseAndFocus
AddToFunc RaiseAndFocus
+ I Focus
+ I Raise

DestroyFunc JOE
AddToFunc JOE
+ I All ($0) RaiseAndFocus
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Exec exec $1 &
Key w A 4 Exec virtualbox --startvm windowsXP

